537
00:46:58,219 --> 00:46:59,820
[SPEAKER_03] Kako je to osjećaj?

538
00:46:59,820 --> 00:47:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] Neke situacije.

539
00:47:01,280 --> 00:47:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

540
00:47:02,519 --> 00:47:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] To možda izgleda onako.

541
00:47:04,760 --> 00:47:06,460
[SPEAKER_03] Da imam još puno toga za raditi.

542
00:47:06,460 --> 00:47:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

543
00:47:07,679 --> 00:47:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što sam rekla, i za mene ipak 30 godina rada.

544
00:47:12,019 --> 00:47:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] Nije.

545
00:47:13,300 --> 00:47:14,980
[SPEAKER_03] Kamerman će nam se ugušiti.

546
00:47:14,980 --> 00:47:15,300
[SPEAKER_03] Šta je mi?

547
00:47:15,300 --> 00:47:24,019
